# 📄 ABOUT PAGE

`/about`

## Headline

About Nangura Social Care

## Subheading

Professional psychological support rooted in compassion, confidentiality, and clinical integrity.

## Body Copy

Nangura Social Care is a professional counselling practice serving individuals, couples, children, and families across Namibia.

Founded and led by a UNAM-trained Social Worker with years of professional experience, this practice is built on one simple belief:

Every person deserves to be heard with dignity and respect.

With experience working within structured health environments and supporting diverse communities, Nangura Social Care offers counselling that is:

• Ethical
• Confidential
• Evidence-based
• Culturally aware
• Grounded in professional standards

Whether you are navigating stress, relationship challenges, trauma, emotional overwhelm, or life transitions, sessions are designed to provide structured guidance and a safe environment for meaningful progress.

In-person sessions are available in Tsumeb, Oshikoto Region.
Online sessions are available nationwide across Namibia.

Seeking support is not a sign of weakness. It is a step toward clarity and stability.

